### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001

### OpenAPI Spec
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

### Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice"
}

### Create User - Invalid (Empty Name)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### Get User by ID (use created user ID from above)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/a4ab73e4-a5ff-4f6a-bb49-021a2e6607eb
Accept: application/json

### Get User by ID - Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

### Get All Outbox Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/outbox
Accept: application/json
